{"tid":224995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張宇人斥最低工資加幅高　食肆結業潮料加速","createTime":"2017-05-01T12:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T04:32:47.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eec0afba53ae0e0da1620c06a5332424ce441af2","tid":224995,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"行政會議通過最低工資水平，由每小時32.5元調升至34.5元，增幅6.2%。行會成員、飲食界立法會議員張宇人批評加幅高，對飲食業界造成非常大衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n張宇人說，在飲食業人手短缺情況下提高最低工資，或會令僱員轉投其他較舒適的工種，加劇員工流失，同時令業界蝕本的情況加劇。<br />\n<br />\n張宇人提及，今年的結業潮或會提早至3月，又說業界過往都難以維持生意，相信今年結業潮有機會加速。<br />\n<br />\n他說政府的做法偏離業界愈來愈遠，政策衝著飲食業而來，但從未提供援助。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由第一次有最低工資講到而家，到底執咗幾多間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"3c85962cf0e69746a8b8e17a2b21e29bed1fc411","tid":224995,"uid":14510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"食肆執笠9成係因為惡性競爭同鋪租不停加導致, <br />\n有邊間真係因為最低工資而執?<br />\non99"},{"pid":"c797375b80c3499243aacbd2d80f76c0ca82600a","tid":224995,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"加租果時又唔會講<br />\n業主食魚翅緊要過打工仔食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82637488e0d77813cab67996bce9780906183b64","tid":224995,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"張宇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd9137f300f40b1d625b07cb97e26f6651c2deb","tid":224995,"uid":36056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"租金千千萬萬咁加又唔講"},{"pid":"8c09cb422abf14ec26f424495bfc8c16d1d5a17e","tid":224995,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"食人唔